  "commit_message": "fix: Warn and ignore invalid `CYPRESS_env` and `CYPRESS_expose` values (#33945)\n\n* fix: warn instead of silently ignore when CYPRESS_ env var override fails validation\n\nWhen a CYPRESS_-prefixed env var that maps to a known config key (e.g.\nCYPRESS_env) contains an invalid value, the value was previously consumed\nby matchesConfigKey and then silently discarded because parseEnv's return\nvalue overwrites any side-effect on cfg. The user had no indication their\noverride was ignored.\n\nThis fix valida",
